  "keyFeatures": [
    "Grammar-based API for creating publication-quality tables in R",
    "Multi-format output: HTML, PDF, Word, PowerPoint, RTF, Grid Graphics",
    "Rich text formatting: bold, italic, color, font, highlight per cell",
    "Cell merging (horizontal and vertical) for complex layouts",
    "Built-in themes: vanilla, booktabs, APA, zebra, box, and more",
    "Statistical model and summary table generation via summarizor and tabulator",
    "Seamless R Markdown and Quarto integration with knitr chunk options",
    "Mini graphics in cells: minibar, lollipop, linerange, ggplot2 plots",
    "Captions with auto-numbering and cross-references",
    "Global defaults system for consistent styling across documents"
  ],
